{"tid":1169633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翻車魚被海獅啃光腹部　遲鈍到都沒感覺","createTime":"2019-05-24T13:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T15:59:41.000Z","uid":32511,"like":125,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"23bda5f2811100ca1d5f64d9ec9b8fea7da3949b","tid":1169633,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/05/24/20190524090426-8d4acfeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F20190524090426-8d4acfeb.jpg&h=f6be2528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「翻車魚」又稱曼波魚，這種魚體型雖然巨大，但個性卻相當溫馴，甚至遲鈍到連被吃了一口，還是沒有反擊能力，影片曝光後，讓許多人十分震撼！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/05/24/20190524090432-331ab78e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F20190524090432-331ab78e.jpg&h=f5795d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大自然生存法則「弱肉強食」眾所周知，野生動物攝影師赫爾曼(Richard Herrmann)日前在美國加州聖地牙哥外海捕捉到這一幕，讓全球相當震撼！只見影片中，一尾約3公尺長的翻車魚，粗估重量達2噸重，遭到海獅攻擊，海獅迅速地衝向翻車魚，朝牠的腹部撕咬一大塊肉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/05/24/20190524090414-5cf03f2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F20190524090414-5cf03f2d.jpg&h=372ddc04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於翻車魚身形短又厚，沒有腹鰭，主要是靠背鰭和臀鰭在水中前行，但也造成牠們在移動速度十分緩慢，不僅容易被漁民捕到，反應力也相當遲鈍，難逃被其他生物攻擊的命運。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/05/24/20190524090420-13f4dae9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F20190524090420-13f4dae9.jpg&h=6b9baa5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只見這隻被海獅攻擊的翻車魚，腹部一大塊肉被狠狠地咬下，但仍悠哉地在海裡游泳，絲毫沒有反抗的能力。 據了解，雖然翻車魚存活率低，但繁殖能力強，一次可以生產3億顆卵，但反應過於遲鈍，再加上漁民不當捕撈，導致近幾年數量急速銳減，因此世界自然保護聯盟(IUCN)2015年時將翻車魚列入「瀕危物種紅色名錄(Red List)」物種。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gMsCHq5a3oo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgMsCHq5a3oo&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=371c80be\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gMsCHq5a3oo</a>"},{"pid":"28020b8862f281e0e27691761d70e06f12fb182c","tid":1169633,"uid":5220,"like":704,"dislike":5,"score":699,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"Molamola <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb147f2784e296367dc8b486b410e4b02e05abf","tid":1169633,"uid":2654,"like":1166,"dislike":4,"score":1162,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"香港人=翻車魚"},{"pid":"67f271140a6ecf9ee69b20f8ad48c30b7742771b","tid":1169633,"uid":93096,"like":31,"dislike":9,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:45:29.000Z","msg":"好食咩"},{"pid":"3a8d8bb80819817a9096bcc0c083f823295b63c3","tid":1169633,"uid":57410,"like":280,"dislike":4,"score":276,"quote":{"pid":"4bb147f2784e296367dc8b486b410e4b02e05abf","tid":1169633,"uid":2654,"like":1166,"dislike":4,"score":1162,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"香港人=翻車魚"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:46:34.000Z","msg":"唔係 有人好大反應 另一班人會屌鳩大反應個班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0bed9e2348f08df0be6600e518d94d3127cb3f","tid":1169633,"uid":8219,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"67f271140a6ecf9ee69b20f8ad48c30b7742771b","tid":1169633,"uid":93096,"like":31,"dislike":9,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:45:29.000Z","msg":"好食咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:46:43.000Z","msg":"係台灣食到無曬"},{"pid":"b2bb85c779585b3dcbbb96404c63383d06650eea","tid":1169633,"uid":10125,"like":105,"dislike":1,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:50:20.000Z","msg":"2噸重 咁誇張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46defaf3c69337877d7065a79a2b68c6b4d6c98f","tid":1169633,"uid":103521,"like":206,"dislike":1,"score":205,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"點解可以係